---
title: "Sleep Dealer"
format: "film"
category: "s"
yearReleased: "2008"
author: "Alex Rivera"
---
Interesting vision of resistance in a Mexico still exploited by the United States, but by means of remote robotic control without immigration from the south. Categorised as a notable contribution to Latinxfuturism, it has been favourably referenced on anarchist Facebook pages.
